    "Id": "chassisdef_boyyi_BYI-1",
    "Name": "Boyyi",
    "Details": "The Boyyi 1 is built for speed and firepower, centered around a massive XXL engine and an active probe mounted deep in its torso. This grants speeds comparable to many combat VTOLs, with a supercharger enabling short bursts of even greater velocity, albeit with high risk. Armed with Improved Heavy Lasers for close combat, the Boyyi excels in detection, evasion, and pursuit, thanks to intensive training by Stone Lion reconnaissance pilots. Though some Coyote pilots seek more “Clan-like” assignments, the invasion’s urgency has kept them committed, making the Boyyi a versatile and vital asset in the Touman’s operations.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Advanced Optics</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#0064e6>Used with permission from Aries Games and Miniatures.</color></b>",
