  "StockRole": "Fast Recon",
  "YangsThoughts": "When Clan Coyote prepared to return to the Inner Sphere, they committed to a do-or-die campaign: either secure territory or be broken. The Boyyi - meaning roadrunner in Terran Native American Zuni - reflects this harsh philosophy. Its design is resource-intensive and limited in numbers, created to serve as a superior recon presence on enemy worlds. This strategy and other invasion policies have left the Coyotes’ Clan Homeworld territories severely depleted of resources.",
